parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive brake pad wear and squeaking can lead to reduced braking performance, increased stopping distances, and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: Squeaking or rubbing sounds when braking
brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Failure and Loss of Control
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially result in injuries or fatalities.
Transmission problems can cause loss of power, difficulty shifting gears, and potentially lead to accidents or stalling.
symptoms: O2 sensor or catalytic converter problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the crankshaft pulley bolt can cause the belt and pulley to fall out, leading to engine damage, coolant leaks, and loss of power, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the belt and pulley fall out
the engine makes a clicking noise

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine hesitation and stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or shut off, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle stalls when trying to accelerate

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden acceleration can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.

The failure of the door hinges can cause the doors to become difficult to open or close, leading to misalignment and damage to the door and surrounding body panels. This can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Doors are difficult to open or close
interior lights and door ajar lights stay on
cracks develop on the lower hinge of the door
doors will not line up properly to close.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The separation of the hood and hood skeleton can cause the hood to become loose and potentially fly open while driving, obstructing the driver's view and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Hood and hood skeleton become separated
glue holding the two parts together fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants are not properly protected.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended deployment of airbags can cause unexpected distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and can also cause damage to the vehicle.
